xotsVMJQ","ref":"Lev.24.1","text":"And the LORD spake unto Moses, saying,","year":-1490},{"id":"recYoDCSBVgp5WCa0","ref":"Lev.24.2","text":"Command the children of Israel, that they bring unto thee pure oil olive beaten for the light, to cause the lamps to burn continually.","year":-1490},{"id":"recgMv2erbJFOsDX4","ref":"Lev.24.3","text":"Without the vail of the testimony, in the tabernacle of the congregation, shall Aaron order it from the evening unto the morning before the LORD continually: it shall be a statute for ever in your generations.","year":-1490},{"id":"recejHGqPBK00AbOF","ref":"Lev.24.4","text":"He shall order the lamps upon the pure candlestick before the LORD continually.","year":-1490},{"id":"rec0q9TpvoTGffu1C","ref":"Lev.24.5","text":"And thou shalt take fine flour, and bake twelve cakes thereof: two tenth deals shall be in one cake.","year":-1490},{"id":"receHSwL9JdfdGx5U","ref":"Lev.24.6","text":"And thou shalt set them in two rows, six on a row, upon the pure table before the LORD.","year":-1490},{"id":"rec9Fe67Wcs0hiwUM","ref":"Lev.24.7","text":"And thou shalt put pure frankincense upon each row, that it may be on the bread for a memorial, even an offering made by fire unto the LORD.","year":-1490},{"id":"rec5aeGS1ko0ImuiL","ref":"Lev.24.8","text":"Every sabbath he shall set it in order before the LORD continually, being taken from the children of Israel by an everlasting covenant.","year":-1490}]}
